info.label: Number of individuals in the cohort.
A 2-dose schedule is advised for both vaccine types in the current vaccination programme. Total includes both Dose 1 and Dose 2 vaccines administered.
Number of individuals who have received the vaccine
Percentage of cohort having received vaccination. Percent coverage is calculated using the NRS Scotland 2019 mid-year population estimates.
Cumulative number of individuals who have received the vaccine.
Cumulative percentage of cohor having received vaccination. Percent coverage is calculated using the NRS Scotland 2019 mid-year populations by age and sex.
